Item added to your cart Company Veowork Technology Co.,Ltd. Founded in February 2018, Veowork is headquartered in Shenzhen and has office in Hong Kong. It is a technology-based company focusing on the research and development, technical services and manufacture of audio visual collaboration solutions. Focusing on the development of AI Audio Video products, Veowork has core technologies in AI algorithms, image processing, audio processing, PTZ control and wireless image transmission. The main product lines include face liveness detection and face recognition cameras, video conferencing cameras, audio and video switchers, wireless transmittter and receiver etc. Veowork integrated market-leading biometrics technologies into cameras for Access control/Self-service Terminals such as ATM/VTM/RTM/Kiosk/Charging facilities/etc. Veowork has always been based on the principle of "Customer First", and its partners are located in North America, the EU, Southeast Asia and other regional markets.
